'''基于内核的虚拟机'''（{{lang-en|'''K'''ernel-based '''V'''irtual '''M'''achine}}，縮寫為{{lang|en|'''KVM'''}}）是一种用於[[Linux內核|Linux內核]]中的虛擬化基礎设施，可將Linux內核轉化為一個[[Hypervisor|虚拟机监视器]]。KVM于2007年2月5日被導入Linux 2.6.20核心中。<ref name="2620notes">{{cite web
 | url = http://kernelnewbies.org/Linux_2_6_20#head-bca4fe7ffe454321118a470387c2be543ee51754
 | title = Linux kernel 2.6.20, Section 2.2. Virtualization support through KVM
 | date = 2007-02-05
 | accessdate = 2014-06-16
 | website = kernelnewbies.org
 | archive-date = 2015-07-16
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150716045159/http://kernelnewbies.org/Linux_2_6_20#head-bca4fe7ffe454321118a470387c2be543ee51754
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>KVM需要支持{{tsl|en|hardware-assisted virtualization|硬件辅助虚拟化|硬件虚拟化拓展}}特性的处理器。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.linux-kvm.org/page/FAQ#What_do_I_need_to_use_KVM.3F |title=KVM FAQ: What do I need to use KVM? |accessdate=2018-08-14 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125162526/https://www.linux-kvm.org/page/FAQ#What_do_I_need_to_use_KVM.3F |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

KVM起初支持[[X86|x86]]平台处理器并随后被[[移植_(軟體)|移植]]到了{{tsl|en|IBM ESA/390|IBM ESA/390|S/390}}、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://article.gmane.org/gmane.comp.emulators.kvm.devel/2570 |title=Gmane - Mail To News And Back Again<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-09-16 |archive-date=2007-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929124348/http://article.gmane.org/gmane.comp.emulators.kvm.devel/2570 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>[[PowerPC|PowerPC]]、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.gmane.org/gmane.comp.emulators.kvm.devel/2595 |title=Gmane Loom<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-09-16 |archive-date=2007-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929103042/http://news.gmane.org/gmane.comp.emulators.kvm.devel/2595 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和[[IA-64|IA-64]]平台上。在3.9内核合并时也导入了[[ARM架構|ARM]]移植版。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://columbia.github.com/linux-kvm-arm |title=KVM/ARM Open Source Project |access-date=2018-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130310052146/http://columbia.github.com/linux-kvm-arm/ |archive-date=2013-03-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

在KVM上可以运行诸多客户操作系统，包括Linux的诸多发行版、BSD、[[Solaris|Solaris]]、[[Microsoft_Windows|Windows]]、[[Haiku|Haiku]]、[[ReactOS|ReactOS]]、[[貝爾實驗室九號計畫|Plan 9]]、{{tsl|en|AROS Research Operating System|AROS研究操作系统|AROS研究操作系统}}<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.linux-kvm.org/page/Guest_Support_Status | title = KVM wiki: Guest support status | accessdate = 2007-05-27 | archive-date = 2020-11-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201125162506/https://www.linux-kvm.org/page/Guest_Support_Status | dead-url = no }}</ref>和[[MacOS|OS X]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.contrib.andrew.cmu.edu/~somlo/OSXKVM/|title=Running Mac OS X as a QEMU/KVM Guest|accessdate=2014-08-20|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108141601/http://www.contrib.andrew.cmu.edu/~somlo/OSXKVM/|dead-url=no}}</ref>除此之外，还支持Android 2.2、GNU/Hurd<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gnu.org/software/hurd/hurd/status.html |title=status |publisher=Gnu.org |date= |accessdate=2014-02-12 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030809/https://www.gnu.org/software/hurd/hurd/status.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>（Debian K16）、[[MINIX_3|Minix]] 3.1.2a、Solaris 10 U3和Darwin 8.0.1，而其他操作系统或新版操作系统都支持KVM，仅仅存在一些限制而已。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.linux-kvm.org/page/Guest_Support_Status |title=Guest Support Status - KVM |publisher=Linux-kvm.org |date= |accessdate=2014-02-12 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125162506/https://www.linux-kvm.org/page/Guest_Support_Status |dead-url=no }}</ref>

VirtIO{{tsl|en|Paravirtualization|半虚拟化|半虚拟化}} 在Linux、OpenBSD、<ref>{{cite web|url=https://man.openbsd.org/virtio.4|title=OpenBSD man page virtio(4)|accessdate=2018-02-04|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112043003/http://man.openbsd.org/virtio.4|dead-url=no}}</ref>FreeBSD、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://people.freebsd.org/~kuriyama/virtio/|title=virtio binary packages for FreeBSD|accessdate=2012-10-29|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929051237/https://people.freebsd.org/~kuriyama/virtio/|dead-url=no}}</ref> NetBSD、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://netbsd.gw.com/cgi-bin/man-cgi?virtio++NetBSD-current |title=NetBSD man page virtio(4) |accessdate=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2019-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191113035952/https://netbsd.gw.com/cgi-bin/man-cgi?virtio++NetBSD-current |dead-url=no }}</ref>Windows上支持对部分设备的{{tsl|en|Paravirtualization|半虚拟化|半虚拟化}}。这项特性支持半虚拟化的网卡、半虚拟化的磁盘控制器、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://linux-iscsi.org/wiki/vHost |title=SCSI target for KVM wiki |publisher=linux-iscsi.org |date=2012-08-07 |accessdate=2012-08-12 |archive-date=2020-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605120413/http://linux-iscsi.org/wiki/VHost |dead-url=no }}</ref>用于调整客户端内存使用的气球设备（Balloon device）和使用[[獨立計算環境簡單協議|獨立計算環境簡單協議]]的VGA图形接口。

